<div class="card"><h2>授权登录设置</h2><p class="muted">配置妖火账号 OAuth 登录。回调地址请在应用后台填写：<b><?=h($cfg['yh_oauth_callback'])?></b></p></div><div class="card form" style="max-width:760px"><form method="post"><input type="hidden" name="csrf_token" value="<?=h($_SESSION['csrf_token']??'')?>"><label style="display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:center"><input style="width:auto;min-height:auto" type="checkbox" name="yh_oauth_enabled" value="1" <?=$cfg['yh_oauth_enabled']==='1'?'checked':''?>> 开启授权登录入口</label><label style="display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:center"><input style="width:auto;min-height:auto" type="checkbox" name="yh_oauth_register_enabled" value="1" <?=$cfg['yh_oauth_register_enabled']==='1'?'checked':''?>> 允许授权注册新用户</label><p class="muted">关闭授权注册后，已授权登录过的用户仍可登录；未授权登录过的用户会提示已关闭授权登录。</p><label>应用 ID / appId</label><input name="yh_oauth_app_id" value="<?=h($cfg['yh_oauth_app_id'])?>" placeholder="appId"><label>应用密钥 / appKey</label><input name="yh_oauth_app_key" type="password" value="<?=h($cfg['yh_oauth_app_key'])?>" placeholder="appKey"><label>回调地址</label><input name="yh_oauth_callback" value="<?=h($cfg['yh_oauth_callback'])?>"><p class="actions"><button class="btn green">保存授权设置</button><a class="btn" href="index.php?r=admin">返回后台</a></p></form></div>
